('ban ip', 8192, 8838608, 'Syntax: .ban ip $ip $time $reason\r\nBans given ip (with accounts on this ip) for given time with given reason.\r\neg: .ban IP 3213.321321.2 3d plum plum\r\nFor perm type -1 in $time.'),
