('damage', 8192, 8838608, 'Syntax: .damage $damage_amount [$school [$spellid]]\r\nApply $damage to target. If not $school and $spellid provided then this flat clean melee damage without any modifiers. If $school provided then damage modified by armor reduction (if school physical), and target absorbing modifiers and result applied as melee damage to target. If spell provided then damage modified and applied as spell damage. $spellid can be shift-link.'),
