('go zonexy', 8192, 8838608, 'Syntax: .go zonexy #x #y [#zone]\nTeleport player to point with (#x,#y) client coordinates at ground(water) level in zone #zoneid or current zone if #zoneid not provided. You can look up zone using .lookup area $namepart'),
